title: Core DAO nomination for: Mo Ma @degenmoma
body:
Telegram Discussion Link : https://t.me/acryptos9/12746

Mo Ma has been our specialist for asking „dumb questions“. He is eager to develop a solid technical understanding and is teaching people everything he learned. 

What he could do:
- Research and track interesting developments on BSC and Ethereum that could be useful for our decision making process and roadmap
- Negotiate incoming or outgoing proposals, looking for talented freelancers or team members for our overall development work
- Connecting to the broader community, building valuable connections

Telegram: @degenmoma
